{"word":"περικήδομαι","slug":"περικήδομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περικήδομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to be very anxious about</i> a person, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:— <el>π. τινι βιότου</el> <i>to take care of</i> a living for him, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}